window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Always the Dungeon Master, never the jail keeper. </b></p> <p>Juniper Smith is trapped in a prison that seems to be of his own design. Everywhere he looks are bits and pieces of the game worlds he used to make back on Earth.</p> <p>Now, he finds himself on the run from the law and helping out criminals, looking for magical solutions to centuries-old magical spirits trapped in bottles.&nbsp;Can he trust an elf that's been locked away since the bad old days of the Second Empire?</p> <p>Danger lurks around every corner, and trust is hard to come by, even within the party that grows more like family with every passing day.</p>"; 
